WEBVTT

00:01.334 --> 00:03.071
WALSH:
So this is what it is.

00:03.104 --> 00:04.804
Talking about
communication.

00:04.838 --> 00:07.740
Talking about language.
Not the same thing.

00:07.775 --> 00:09.676
It's about
inspiration,

00:09.710 --> 00:11.512
not the idea,
but the moment

00:11.544 --> 00:14.314
before the idea,
when it's total.

00:14.348 --> 00:17.350
When it blossoms in your mind
and connects to everything.

00:17.385 --> 00:19.219
It's about the thoughts
and experiences

00:19.253 --> 00:21.254
that we don't
have a word for.

00:21.289 --> 00:23.824
A demonstration.

00:23.856 --> 00:25.259
Buffy Summers.

00:25.292 --> 00:27.161
(students murmuring)

00:27.195 --> 00:28.896
