00:38.206 --> 00:40.073
Lie down on my desk.

00:40.107 --> 00:41.942
What?

00:41.975 --> 00:44.112
Go ahead. You're perfectly safe.

00:44.145 --> 00:46.579
(students murmuring)

00:55.655 --> 00:58.491
Riley, if you could oblige.

00:59.759 --> 01:02.295
A demonstration, right?

01:02.329 --> 01:04.831
Be a good boy.

01:17.144 --> 01:20.548
