01:20.581 --> 01:25.018
Don't worry. If I kiss you,
it'll make the sun go down.

01:41.668 --> 01:45.872
(whooshing, wind whistling)

01:53.847 --> 01:56.183
See?

01:58.686 --> 02:01.454
Fortune favors the brave.

02:01.489 --> 02:03.891
