02:12.832 --> 02:16.637
* Can't even shout,
can't even cry *

02:16.670 --> 02:20.341
* The gentlemen are coming by

02:20.373 --> 02:23.143
* Looking in windows,
knocking on doors *

02:23.176 --> 02:27.881
